The '''Uscru Entertainment District''', also simply known as the '''Entertainment District''', was the entertainment area located in the [[Coruscant Underworld|lower levels]] of the [[Uscru District]] on the [[planet]] [[Coruscant]].

==Description==
The Uscru Entertainment District was the [[Coruscant Underworld|lower levels]] area of the [[planet]] [[Coruscant]]'s [[Uscru District]].<ref name="SWCL2016" /> It housed clubs and bars that hosted gambling, drinking and various other entertainment. The area had large crowds, constant traffic, and lit advertisement boards that announced the various services available. It made for a perfect area for fugitives to escape into and for criminals or those who did want attention to sell illicit goods and wares. It was the site of the popular [[Outlander Club]], where people could bet on sporting events that were going on around [[the galaxy]].<ref name="Ultimate SW" />

==History==
[[File:UscruEntertainmentDistrict.png|thumb|300px|View of the district]]
Just before the [[Clone Wars]], [[Jedi Knight]] [[Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Padawan]] [[Anakin Skywalker]] pursued [[bounty hunter]] [[Zam Wesell]] via [[airspeeder]] through the Coruscant [[skylane]]s before Skywalker forced Wesell to crash into the streets of the Uscru Entertainment District. He chased her to the entrance of the [[Outlander Club]], where he met up with Kenobi and the two [[Jedi]] found and revealed the shapeshifting nature of the [[bounty]] hunter. However, before Wesell could reveal the identity of her benefactor, she was [[Death|killed]] via a [[poison dart]] by [[Jango Fett]], the bounty hunter who had hired her to [[Plot to assassinate Senator Amidala|assassinate]] [[Senator]] [[Padmé Amidala]].<ref name="AotC">{{Film|II}}</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
[[Industrial Light & Magic]] model maker [[Grant Imahara]] worked on building the miniature set of the Coruscant streets in the Uscru Entertainment District.<ref name="Ultimate SW" />

''[[Star Wars: Absolutely Everything You Need to Know]]'' and [[Star Wars: Complete Locations (2016)|''Star Wars: Complete Locations'']] both state that the Uscru Entertainment District was located in Coruscant's lower levels. In ''[[Ultimate Star Wars]]'' and its online [[Databank (2014-)|Databank]] entry, the Galaxies Opera House is listed as being in the upper levels of the Uscru District with ''Ultimate Star Wars'' making a distinction in listing locations as being in either the upper levels of the Uscru District or in the lower levels of the "Entertainment District." As such, the Entertainment District is considered to be part of the larger "Uscru District" yet comprising the district's lower levels.

